{"tid":1395043,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好諗住買張現金卷 就可以推翻呢個腐敗政權","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:11.000Z","uid":96675,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01e479149960c192194dafafa2fd5bc067fb918e","tid":1395043,"uid":96675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:31:12.000Z","msg":"係 前線係缺物資<br />\n但最缺嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地</span>啊<br />\n<br />\n假如你買張卷 會令每次上街都多一個人嘅 前線一定會好開心 <br />\n假如你買張卷 會令罷工多兩個人擺嘅 大家都會好感謝<br />\n<br />\n但事實係唔會啊<br />\n<br />\n唔好用買卷黎比藉口自己可以放手比哂其他人出黎 可以乜都唔使理 <br />\n<br />\n你唔係助養細路啊 你係同我地一齊救緊香港啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">八月五號 全民罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"07cc99d1ab9e5513087941e0b68b28a29ee025ff","tid":1395043,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"04dd20337b9bd4a2979eb20c9699bad65778b547","tid":1395043,"uid":292478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7611dbc850c6f913c871b05a974bb9621b18eb95","tid":1395043,"uid":270571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"入黎我話你聽班小朋友其實最急要咩物資<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394947</a>"}]}